employ
Discworld lord help
employ 


.SH Name
.SI 5
employ - Promote someone to creator status.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
employ <name>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
The employ command allows you to promote a player to the heady ranks of
creatordom.  Their playerfile will be backed up to /save/creators, and they
will need to su to get their creator object.  A room will be created for them
in /w/<their_name>/workroom, and a mail (/doc/creator/concepts/creator_doc.txt) 
will be sent out to them.
.EP

.SH Examples:
.SI 5
employ draktest
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
dismiss 
.EP
